Follow these steps to set up and run the project using Docker:

1. Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/Development-Eghai/hiring_backend.git

cd hiring_backend

2. Build and Start Services
Run the following command to build the Docker images and start the containers in detached mode:

docker-compose up --build -d

3. Check That Everything Is Running
To confirm your services are up:

docker ps


4. Stop the Containers
To bring everything down when you're done:

docker-compose down










